  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlphaMap
    This class serves to build an alpha (texture) map given heightmap data.
    ColorMath
    This utilities class handles color-related computation
    ColorVector
    This class defines a Vector to represent a point in 2-space.
    GameAppState
    This class contains most of the world data for what the user will see, Put this here (NOT in the Main class) because it is much easier to clone, re-attach, and remove App States then it is to modify the Main class.
    HeightMap
    This class is used to build and store data for a height map object.
    Main
    This class contains basic data needed by the entire game.
    Statistics
    This class has a bunch of useful statistical equations that help determine how to analyze heightmaps (avg.
    VectorMath
    This utilities class serves to allow Vector computations beyond those included in the jme3 libraries.
